I"ö<p><strong>Delete container pods stuck in state unknown on kubernetes</strong></p>

<p>Sometime, Pods are stuck in ‚ÄúUnknown‚Äù state. Those pods can‚Äôt deleted. Cluster got into this state when I have been summitting many pods at once.</p>

<p>eg:</p>

<pre><code data-trim="" class="yaml">
NAME                                                              READY     STATUS              RESTARTS   AGE
asdmp-doctor-3477391423-97t2v                                     0/1       Unknown             0          14h
